description:
Maria and Paul, a couple in their forties, travel through Spain with a mutual friend, Claire (Romy Schneider). The couple's daughter is also part of the trip. On their way to madrid, they encounter a man who has killed his own wife and the man she was sleeping with. Maria, discontent in her own marriage, wishes to help the murderer escape from the police. A subplot is Maria's lesbian relationship with Claire.
